on_vote_up" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fquatsch-games.itch.io%2Fmimic-sleuth&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/helpingharry"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-gold.png)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/helpingharry">helpingharry</a></span><span class="post_date" title="2022-04-01 14:13:36"><a href="https://itch.io/post/5681106">1 year ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Here is what I managed to figure out for the red boxes.</p><p>(Spoilers if you want to figure it out yourself)</p><p>1- They appear every ten chests and will have special music</p><p>2- If there is a timer on the side, you just have to check as if its a normal chest and try to get it before the timer runs out.</p><p>3-&nbsp; a secret will appear in the guide book, so check that.</p><p>4- Try clicking on the hinge a few times. If it makes a sound, keep clicking.</p><p>5- If there&#x27;s an exclamation mark, a rocket will be shot and you just have to dodge it.</p><p>I&#x27;ll add more if I discover something else.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fquatsch-games.itch.io%2Fmimic-sleuth&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div id="post-5703635" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:5703635,&quot